From: eloisezhang <eloisezhang@ai-imvision.cn>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 10:49:06 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] FIX: AIC_V3: fix pad C/H tiling selection

WHY:
1. Pad large-shape cases may exceed local memory without tiling.
2. Pad channel tiling alone cannot cover C non-aligned large H cases.
3. Zero-padding tile should use memcpy to avoid unsupported all-zero pad on hardware.

JIRA: #COMPILER-825
TEST: pass in local
Change-Id: I15eb95b6d4bae751d4e580ea5c1117d1409fb85f
Signed-off-by: eloisezhang <eloisezhang@ai-imvision.cn>
